flowchart TD

A[Start Game] --> B[Initialize Board with starting discs]
B --> C[Set CurrentPlayer = Black]

C --> D[Render Board]
D --> E[Check Available Moves for CurrentPlayer]

E -->|No Moves| F[Switch Turn]
F --> G[Check Available Moves for Next Player]
G -->|No Moves for both players| Z[Game Over]

E -->|Moves Available| H[Human Input (row, col)]

H --> I[Validate Move]
I -->|Invalid| D2[Show Error & Ask Again]
D2 --> H

I -->|Valid| J[Place Disc on Board]
J --> K[Flip Opponent Discs]

K --> L[Update Score on Board]
L --> M[Trigger: OnBoardUpdated Action]
M --> N[Trigger: OnTurnChanged Action]

N --> O[Switch Player]
O --> C

Z --> X[Calculate Final Score]
X --> Y[Trigger: OnGameOver Action]
Y --> END[End]
